{"tid":1779583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"輔警敎畜下文","createTime":"2019-12-11T18:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T05:37:29.000Z","uid":190727,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"018a8a573ba23e3712b53b1cd58d720d698f157b","tid":1779583,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"輔警教畜想紅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n校方出咗聲明<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sshEidL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsshEidL.png&h=621dbdf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一堆廢話唔使睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全冇打算處罰<br />\n學校想將件事化淡佢<br />\n深藍校長想保隻狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有學生透露受到校長威脅(校長藍到發黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果將件事搞大嘅就將個名交上教育局<br />\n暫時冇source但係係有幾個現任學生同我講<br />\n以往都有學生受過同樣經歷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9oLiyOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9oLiyOg.png&h=cb8991b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好需要各位手足幫手<br />\n推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要垃圾教育局出嚟回應<br />\n輔助犬隻停職調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c00ca89b608756956f7508ec1cfec156338969","tid":1779583,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5c7ee387a951c05c272f79e90346c89c2cc33c1d","tid":1779583,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d75afc781449662cefd1ee20ea74a338701d6c8","tid":1779583,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:46:53